NK016(ma)008:0: na raka dong sprugs las phyag gi bkol byang bzhugs so //
NK016(ma)008:1: hoh klong chen po stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di ni /
NK016(ma)008:2: don dam par chos kyi dbyings yum gyi mkha' b+ha ga yangs pa'i klong /
NK016(ma)008:3: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor rnam par dag pa na
NK016(ma)008:4: bzhugs pa'i bde bar gshegs pa 'khor rgyal ba rgya
NK016(ma)008:5: mtsho dang bcas pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:7: kun gzhi gsang pa dag pa'i dbyings nas /
NK016(ma)008:8: rang rig pa rang byung gi ye shes /
NK016(ma)008:9: rang shes rig gi rgyal po /
NK016(ma)008:10: yid byed pa po dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi yab /
NK016(ma)008:11: chags med skyon dang bral bas gdan pad+ma la bzhugs pa /
NK016(ma)008:12: sangs rgyas dang sems can mnyam par mkhyen pas phyag mnyam pa'i phyag rgya can /
NK016(ma)008:13: dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi mnga' bdag /
NK016(ma)008:14: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:16: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad don dam par chos kyi dbyings su sdud ma /
NK016(ma)008:17: chos can mtshan ma'i skyon gyis ma gos pas gdan pad+ma la bzhugs pa /
NK016(ma)008:18: kun la khyab par gnas pas phyag mnyam pa'i phyag tshan /
NK016(ma)008:20: dkyil 'khor thams cad bskyed pa'i yum kun tu bzang mo la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:22: chos rnams rnam dag ye nas lhun grub pa'i //
NK016(ma)008:23: bya ba byed dang yid chos rnam par dag /
NK016(ma)008:24: kun bzang yab yum gnyis la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:25: don dam par sems can gyi rnam par shes pa'i phung po gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:26: de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs kyi bdag nyid /
NK016(ma)008:27: mi 'jigs pa seng ge'i khri can /
NK016(ma)008:28: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis skye shi dang 'pho 'gyur gyi rtog pa mi mnga' bas /
NK016(ma)008:30: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje mi bskyod pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:31: don dam par sems can gyi gzugs kyi phung po gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:32: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku'i bdag nyid /
NK016(ma)008:33: stobs glang po che'i khri can me long lta bu'i ye shes kyis kun la dbang sgyur bas /
NK016(ma)008:35: bcom ldan 'das dpal rnam par snang mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:36: don dam par sems can gyi tshor ba'i phung po gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:37: de bzhin gshegs pa'i yon tan gyi bdag nyid /
NK016(ma)008:39: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes las ma g.yos par che ba'i yon tan thams cad 'byung bas /
NK016(ma)008:40: phyag rgya rin po che 'bar ba can /
NK016(ma)008:41: bcom ldan 'das dpal rin chen 'byung ldan la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:42: don dam par sems can gyi 'du shes kyi phung po gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:43: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung gi bdag nyid /
NK016(ma)008:44: mdzes byed rma bya'i khri can /
NK016(ma)008:45: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyis chos thams cad
NK016(ma)008:46: kyi spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid gsal la ma
NK016(ma)008:47: chags par gzigs pas phyag rgya pad+ma can /
NK016(ma)008:48: bcom ldan 'das dpal snang ba mtha' yas la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:49: don dam par sems can gyi 'du byed kyi phung po gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:50: de bzhin gshegs pa'i phrin las kyi bdag nyid /
NK016(ma)008:51: cang byed shang shang te'u'i khri can /
NK016(ma)008:52: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyis phrin las mthar phyin par mdzad pas /
NK016(ma)008:53: phyag rgya rdo rje rgya gram can /
NK016(ma)008:54: bcom ldan 'das dpal don yod grub pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:55: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK016(ma)008:56: gzugs sku 'ja' tshon bzhin du so sor gsal //
NK016(ma)008:57: thabs dang shes rab mchog la mnga' brnyes pa'i //
NK016(ma)008:58: rigs lnga bde bar gshegs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:59: don dam par 'byung ba nam mkha'i ngo bo gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:60: yum chen mo kun tu bzang mo /
NK016(ma)008:61: dus gsum gyis rgyal ba thams cad 'byung ba'i gnas /
NK016(ma)008:62: yum chen mo nam mkha' dbyings phyug ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:63: don dam par 'byung ba sa'i ngo bo gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:64: yum chen mo sangs rgyas spyan ma /
NK016(ma)008:65: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba thams cad bskyed pa'i gzhi /
NK016(ma)008:66: yum chen mo bud+d+ha dbyings phyug ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:67: don dam par 'byung ba chu'i ngo bo gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:68: yum chen mo m+aa ma k+ai /
NK016(ma)008:69: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba rnams kyi yon tan gyi gter 'dzin ma /
NK016(ma)008:70: yum chen mo rin chen dbyings phyug ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:71: don dam par 'byung ba me'i ngo bo gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:72: yum chen mo na bza' dkar mo /
NK016(ma)008:73: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba rnams kyi gsung mchog ma /
NK016(ma)008:74: yum chen mo pad+ma dbyings phyug ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:75: don dam par 'byung ba rlung gi ngo bo gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:76: yum chen mo dam tshig sgrol ma /
NK016(ma)008:77: 'gro ba rnams 'phags pa'i sa bcur sgrol ma /
NK016(ma)008:78: yum chen mo las kyi dbyings phyug ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:79: ngo mtshar pho brang bde bar gshegs pa'i yum //
NK016(ma)008:80: dus gsum sras bcas thams cad bskyed mdzad ma //
NK016(ma)008:81: rigs kyi yum gyur rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:82: don dam par sems can gyi mig gi rnam par shes pa gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:83: byang chub sems dpa' sa'i snying po /
NK016(ma)008:84: 'gro ba rnams bla na med pa'i gnas su bskyed par byed pas /
NK016(ma)008:85: phyag rgya rin po che'i myu gu can /
NK016(ma)008:86: shar phyogs na bzhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:87: don dam par sems can gyi rna ba'i rnam par shes pa gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:88: byang chub sems dpa' nam mkha'i snying po /
NK016(ma)008:89: nyon mongs pa'i rgyun skad cig la gcod pas /
NK016(ma)008:91: lho phyogs kyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:92: don dam par sems can gyi sna'i rnam par shes pa gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:93: byang chub sems dpa' spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug /
NK016(ma)008:94: nyon mongs pa'i skyon gyi ma gos pas /
NK016(ma)008:96: nub phyogs kyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:97: don dam par sems can gyi lce'i rnam par shes par gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:98: byang chub sems dpa' phyag na rdo rje /
NK016(ma)008:99: nyon mongs pa thams cad 'joms par byed pas /
NK016(ma)008:101: byang phyogs kyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:102: don dam par sems can gyi mig gi dbang po gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:103: byang chub sems dpa' byams pa /
NK016(ma)008:104: nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba las skyob pas /
NK016(ma)008:105: phyag rgya klu shing mgo lcog can /
NK016(ma)008:106: shar lho mtshams kyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:107: don dam par sems can gyi rna ba'i dbang po gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:108: byang chub sems dpa' sgrib pa rnam par sel ba /
NK016(ma)008:109: nyon mongs pa chos nyid du mkhyen pas /
NK016(ma)008:111: lho nub mtshams kyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:112: don dam par sems can gyi sna'i dbang po gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:113: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po /
NK016(ma)008:114: nyon mongs pa gnas su dag pa las /
NK016(ma)008:115: dgos 'dod re ba yid bzhin du skong bas /
NK016(ma)008:116: phyag rgya rin po che'i snye ma can /
NK016(ma)008:117: nub byang mtshams kyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:118: don dam par sems can gyi lce'i dbang po gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:120: nyon mongs pa'i zug rngu mi mnga' bar shin tu mdzes pas /
NK016(ma)008:122: byang shar mtshams kyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:123: rnam shes dbang po dag pas thugs dang gsung //
NK016(ma)008:124: bde bar gshegs pa kun gyi sras mchog ste //
NK016(ma)008:125: sems dpa' chen po brgyad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:126: don dam par sems can gyi mig gi yul /
NK016(ma)008:127: gzugs su snang ba gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:129: sku'i mchod pas mnyes par mdzad pa la mi 'gyur bas /
NK016(ma)008:130: phyag rgya rdo rje khu tshur can /
NK016(ma)008:131: rdo rje sgeg mo ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:132: don dam par sems can gyi sna'i yul dri snom pa gnas su dag pa badz+ra m+aa l+ye ste /
NK016(ma)008:133: dri'i mchod pa rgyun mi chad par byed pas /
NK016(ma)008:134: phyag rgya rin po che'i phreng ba can /
NK016(ma)008:135: rdo rje phreng ba ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:136: don dam par sems can gyi rna ba'i yul sgrar grags pa gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:138: sgra'i mchod pas mnyes par byed pas /
NK016(ma)008:140: rdo rje sgra dbyangs ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:141: don dam par sems can gyi lce'i yul ro bro ba gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:143: ro'i mchod pas mnyes par byed pas /
NK016(ma)008:145: rdo rje gar sgyur ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:146: sgeg mo phreng thogs rin chen glu gar can //
NK016(ma)008:147: nam mkha' mnyam pa'i mchod pas rgyal ba mchod //
NK016(ma)008:148: byang chub lha mo'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:149: don dam par sems can gyi dus 'das pa zhes bya ba gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:151: shangs kyi mchod pas mnyes par mdzad pas /
NK016(ma)008:153: rdo rje bdug pa ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:154: don dam par sems can gyi dus da lta ba zhes bya ba gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:156: sku yi mchod pas mnyes par mdzad pas /
NK016(ma)008:158: rdo rje me tog ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:159: don dam par sems can gyi dus ma 'ongs pa zhes bya ba gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:161: spyan gyi mchod pas mnyes par mdzad pas /
NK016(ma)008:163: rdo rje mar me ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:164: don dam par sems can gyi dus ma nges pa zhes bya ba gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:166: ljags byug pa'i mchod pas mnyes par mdzad pas /
NK016(ma)008:168: rdo rje dri chab ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:169: bdug pa me tog mar me dri chab ma //
NK016(ma)008:170: rgyal ba rgya mtsho rnams la mchod 'bul ma //
NK016(ma)008:171: mchod pa'i lha mo rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:172: don dam par sems can gyi lus kyi rnam par shes pa gnas su dag pa //
NK016(ma)008:173: khro bo chen po gshin rje gshed po ste /
NK016(ma)008:174: byams pa chen pos 'gro ba'i don zhe sdang tshar gcod par mdzad pas /
NK016(ma)008:175: phyag rgya n+ri mgo gdengs pa can /
NK016(ma)008:176: shar sgo'i bdag po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:177: don dam par sems can gyi lus kyi reg bya gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:178: khro bo chen po stobs po che ste /
NK016(ma)008:179: snying rje chen pos 'gro ba'i don dug lnga ye shes lngas 'joms par mdzad pas /
NK016(ma)008:180: phyag rgya rdo rje rtse lnga can /
NK016(ma)008:181: lho sgo'i bdag po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:182: don dam par sems can gyi lus kyi dbang po gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:183: khro bo chen po rta mgrin te /
NK016(ma)008:184: dga' ba chen pos 'gro ba'i don thugs rjes mi gtong bar mdzad pas /
NK016(ma)008:185: phyag rgya thod dbyug sbrul gyis dkris pa can /
NK016(ma)008:186: nub sgo'i bdag po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:187: don dam par sems can gyi lus kyi reg bya gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:188: khro bo chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ste /
NK016(ma)008:189: btang snyoms chen pos 'gro ba'i don mthar phyin par mdzad pas /
NK016(ma)008:190: phyag rgya rdo rje rgya gram can /
NK016(ma)008:191: byang sgo'i bdag po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:192: drag shul thabs kyis 'gro ba 'dul mdzad pa /
NK016(ma)008:193: tshad med bzhi ldan sgo bzhi thub par bsrung /
NK016(ma)008:194: mthar byed sgo ba bzhi la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:195: don dam par sems can rtag par lta ba gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:197: 'khor ba'i nyon mongs pa thugs rje 'dzin par byed pas /
NK016(ma)008:199: rdo rje lcags kyu ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:200: don dam par sems can chad par lta ba gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:202: 'khor ba'i nyon mongs pa thugs rjes 'ching bar byed pas /
NK016(ma)008:204: rdo rje zhags pa ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:205: don dam par sems can bdag tu lta ba gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:207: 'khor ba'i nyon mongs pa thugs rjes mi 'chor bar mdzad pas /
NK016(ma)008:209: rdo rje lcags sgrog ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:210: don dam par sems can mtshan mar lta ba gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:212: 'khor ba'i nyon mongs pa thal bar rlog par mdzad pas /
NK016(ma)008:214: rdo rje dril bu ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:215: rtag chad lta 'byin gsang ba yum gyi ngang //
NK016(ma)008:216: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril 'khrol ma //
NK016(ma)008:217: ye shes sgo ma bzhi la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:218: don dam par sems can lha'i 'jig rten du lta ba gnas du dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:220: nyon mongs pa nga rgyal gnas su dag par mdzad pas /
NK016(ma)008:222: lha'i bcom ldan 'das la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:223: don dam par sems can lha ma yin gyi 'jig rten du lta ba gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:224: lha ma yin gyi thub pa ste /
NK016(ma)008:225: nyon mongs pa phrag dog gnas su dag par mdzad pas /
NK016(ma)008:227: lha ma yin gyi bcom ldan 'das la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:228: don dam par sems can mi'i 'jig rten du lta ba gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:230: nyon mongs pa 'dod chags gnas su dag par mdzad pas /
NK016(ma)008:231: phyag rgya gseg shang par bu can /
NK016(ma)008:232: mi'i bcom ldan 'das la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:233: don dam par sems can byol song gi 'jig rten du lta ba gnas du dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:234: byol song gi thub pa ste /
NK016(ma)008:235: nyon mongs pa gti mug gnas su dag par mdzad pas /
NK016(ma)008:236: phyag rgya glegs bam pu ti can /
NK016(ma)008:237: byol song gi bcom ldan 'das la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:238: don dam par sems can yi dwags kyi 'jig rten du lta ba gnas du dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:239: yi dwags kyi thub pa ste /
NK016(ma)008:240: nyon mongs pa ser sna gnas su dag par mdzad pas /
NK016(ma)008:241: phyag rgya rin po che'i sgrom bu can /
NK016(ma)008:242: yi dwags kyi bcom ldan 'das la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:243: don dam par sems can dmyal ba'i 'jig rten du lta ba gnas su dag pa /
NK016(ma)008:245: nyon mongs pa zhe sdang gnas su dag par mdzad pas /
NK016(ma)008:247: dmyal ba'i bcom ldan 'das la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:248: steng 'og phyogs bzhi 'jig rten 'dul ba'i gtso //
NK016(ma)008:249: nyon mongs drug 'joms rgyud drug dag par sbyong //
NK016(ma)008:250: bcom ldan thub pa drug la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:252: rang rig pa thabs kyi rgyal po khro bo thams cad kyi rje btsan chen po /
NK016(ma)008:253: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi spyi dpal /
NK016(ma)008:254: bcom ldan 'das bla na med pa'i dpal chen po che mchog he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:255: rdo rje lta bu'i sku dus gsum du 'gyur ba mi mnga' ba /
NK016(ma)008:256: zhe sdang chen po thabs la mkhas pas dregs pa pho mo'i gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK016(ma)008:257: khro bo thams cad kyi thugs kyi bdag nyid badz+ra he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:258: chos nyid stong pa nyid kyi dbyings nas skye ba med pa'i sku ba rnyes pa /
NK016(ma)008:259: gti mug thabs la mkhas pas ma h+aa de wa'i gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK016(ma)008:260: khro bo thams cad kyi sku'i bdag nyid bud+d+ha he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:261: chos nyid byang chub sems las longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku brnyes pa /
NK016(ma)008:262: nga rgyal chen po thabs la mkhas pas gshin rje'i gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK016(ma)008:263: khro bo thams cad kyi yon tan gyi bdag nyid rat+na he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:264: chos nyid chags pa med pa'i dbyings nas byang chub chen po'i sku brnyes pa /
NK016(ma)008:265: 'dod chags thabs la mkhas pas klu'i gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK016(ma)008:266: khro bo thams cad kyi gsung gi bdag nyid pad+ma he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:267: phrin las grub pa'i dbyings nas sprul pa mchog gi sku brnyes pa /
NK016(ma)008:268: phrag dog thabs la mkhas pas gnod sbyin gyi gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK016(ma)008:269: khro bo thams cad kyi phrin las kyi bdag nyid karma he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:270: sbyor pa'i dbyings nas phyin ci log gi lta ba 'joms pa'i sku brnyes pa /
NK016(ma)008:271: ga na'i thabs la mkhas pas drang srong gi gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK016(ma)008:272: rak+sha he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:273: dam tshig gi dbyings nas myong byed kyi rtog pa 'joms pa'i sku brnyes pa /
NK016(ma)008:274: nyams pa bskang ba'i thabs la mkhas pas srin po'i gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK016(ma)008:275: sa nu he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:276: gsang ba'i dbyings nas skye gnas kyi rtog pa 'joms pa'i sku brnyes pa /
NK016(ma)008:277: mtshan ma'i thabs la mkhas pas rlung lha'i gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK016(ma)008:278: gu h+ya he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:279: sgrol ba'i dbyings nas reg bya'i rtog pa 'joms pa'i sku brnyes pa /
NK016(ma)008:280: ta na'i thabs la mkhas pas /
NK016(ma)008:281: bgegs kyi gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK016(ma)008:282: yak+sha he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:283: 'jig rten 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba //
NK016(ma)008:284: gdug pa 'dul phyir dus las mi 'da' ba'i //
NK016(ma)008:285: dpal chen khrag 'thung rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:286: rang bzhin dag pa'i dbyings nas yum chen mo'i sku brnyes pa /
NK016(ma)008:287: sku dpal du 'bar bas rngam pa'i cha lugs can /
NK016(ma)008:288: gsung dpal du 'bar bas rngam pa'i gdangs skad can /
NK016(ma)008:289: thugs dpal du 'bar bas thugs rje chen po can /
NK016(ma)008:290: dpal 'bar khros pa'i rgyal mo khro mo gnam zhal ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:291: chos nyid dbyings kyi phyag rgya las rnam par thar ba'i sku brnyes pa /
NK016(ma)008:292: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par 'khril bas cha lugs gtso bo dang mthun pa /
NK016(ma)008:293: badz+ra kro d+hi shwa rwi ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:294: mnyam nyid blang dor med pa'i dbyings nas rol pa ye shes kyi sku brnyes pa /
NK016(ma)008:295: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par 'khril bas cha lugs gtso bo dang mthun pa /
NK016(ma)008:296: bud+hakro d+hi shwa r+ai ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:297: byams mgon chos kyi dbyings nas thugs rje ye shes kyi sku brnyes pa /
NK016(ma)008:298: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par 'khril bas cha lugs gtso bo dang mthun pa /
NK016(ma)008:299: rat+na kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:300: chos nyid pad+ma'i dbyings nas skyon bral pad+ma'i sku brnyes pa /
NK016(ma)008:301: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par 'khril bas cha lugs gtso bo dang mthun pa /
NK016(ma)008:302: pad+ma kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:303: las rab rol ba'i dbyings nas don grub mchog gi sku brnyes pa /
NK016(ma)008:304: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par 'khril bas cha lugs gtso bo dang mthun pa /
NK016(ma)008:305: karma kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:306: drod las skyes pa 'joms pa las sprul pa ste /
NK016(ma)008:307: rak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:308: mngal las skyes pa 'joms pa las sprul pa ste /
NK016(ma)008:309: sa na kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:310: bardzusa nas skyes pa 'joms pa las sprul pa ste /
NK016(ma)008:311: gu h+ya kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:312: sgo nga las skyes pa 'joms pa las sprul pa ste /
NK016(ma)008:313: yak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:314: khro mo dbang phyug sku la 'khril mdzad cing //
NK016(ma)008:315: mkha' 'gro mi bzad 'bar ba'i sprin 'phro ma //
NK016(ma)008:316: gdug pa 'dul mdzad yum rnams la phyag 'tshal //
NK016(ma)008:317: khro mo sngon mo bam dbyug 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:318: goo r+ai ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:319: khro mo ser mo mda' gzhi 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:320: tsoo r+ai ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:321: khro mo dmar mo chu srin 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:322: pra mo h+aa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:323: khro mo mthing nag rdo rje 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:324: bee ta l+ai la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:325: khro mo dmar ser byis rgyu 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:327: khro mo ljang gu dung khrag 'thung //
NK016(ma)008:329: khro mo nag mo byis snying za //
NK016(ma)008:330: sma sha n+ai la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:331: khro mo ser skya mchog lus 'dral //
NK016(ma)008:333: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na //
NK016(ma)008:334: ye shes sku mchog 'jigs byed slas su bzhugs //
NK016(ma)008:335: khro mo chen mo brgyad la sid+ha kha ro bsnol ser seng //
NK016(ma)008:336: seng gdong ma la b+y+aa g+h+ri gnas lta bsnol dmar stag /
NK016(ma)008:337: stag gdong ma la sri g+aal nag mo byis ldag wa //
NK016(ma)008:338: wa gdong ma la shwa na 'dral lta mthing ga spyang /
NK016(ma)008:339: spyang gdong ma la gri d+ha mgrin dmar rgyu 'dren rgod //
NK016(ma)008:340: rgod gdong ma la kang+ka zhing phrag snar mgo ring /
NK016(ma)008:341: dur bya'i gdong mar k+aa ka kha ro b+han gri nag /
NK016(ma)008:342: bya rog gdong mar phyag u l+au rdor dbyug mthing tshogs 'ug 'ug gdong ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:343: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK016(ma)008:344: 'dod dgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK016(ma)008:345: phra men chen mo brgyad la sgo ma sngon mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:346: rta gdong ma la sgo ma nag mo zhags pa 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:347: phag gdong ma la sgo ma dmar mo lcags sgrog 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:348: seng gdong ma la sgo ma ljang gu dril bu 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:349: spyang gdong ma la rdo rje gdong mo pho nya mgyogs ma bzhi //
NK016(ma)008:350: shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi thub par bsrung //
NK016(ma)008:351: sgo skyong khro mo bzhi la rnal 'byor dmar ser tri shul 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:352: g.yag gdong ma la rnal 'byor dmar skya rtse lnga 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:353: sbrul gdong ma la rnal 'byor ser nag dbyug sdigs 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:354: gzig gdong ma la rnal 'byor dkar dmar dung dmar 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:355: sre mong gdong mar rnal 'byor ser mo 'khor lo 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:356: pha wam gdong mar rnal 'byor dmar skya bam dbyug 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:357: dred gdong ma la rnal 'byor dmar mo rgyu zhags 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:358: dom gyi gdong dmar rnal 'byor sngon mo bum pa 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:359: chu srin gdong mar rnal 'byor sngo skya pun+da 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:360: sdig pa'i gdong mar rnal 'byor nag mo thod rlon 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:361: khra gdong ma la rnal 'byor dmar nag rgyu zhags 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:362: wa gdong ma la rnal 'byor nag mo bam chen 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:363: stag gdong ma la rnal 'byor dmar mo khog chen 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:364: rgod gdong ma la rnal 'byor dmar nag rdor dbyug 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:365: rta gdong ma la rnal 'byor dkar dmar b+han+d+ha 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:366: khyung gdong ma la rnal 'byor dmar ser byis bam 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:367: khyi gdong ma la rnal 'byor dkar dmar pad+ma 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:368: pu shud gdong mar rnal 'byor dmar skya ba dan 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:369: sha ba'i gdong mar rnal 'byor ljang nag rnge'u chung 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:370: spyang gdong ma la rnal 'byor dmar ser me sgron 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:371: skyin gdong ma la rnal 'byor ljang ser mche ba 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:372: phag gdong ma la rnal 'byor ljang sngon dung khrag 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:373: khwa gdong ma la rnal 'byor dmar ljang bam chen 'dzin /
NK016(ma)008:374: ba lang gdong mar rnal 'byor ljang nag bdud rtsi 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:375: sbrul gdong ma la rnal 'byor nag mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:376: khu byug gdong mar rnal 'byor sngon mo rgyu zhags 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:377: ra gdong ma la rnal 'byor dmar mo lcags sgrog 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:378: seng gdong ma la rnal 'byor ljang nag dril bu 'dzin //
NK016(ma)008:379: skya ka'i gdong mar dpal gyi 'khor tshogs badz+ra +aa ra l+ai //
NK016(ma)008:380: mkha' la shugs 'gro ma tshogs dbang phyug ma //
NK016(ma)008:381: rnam 'byor nyi shu brgyad la 'dod pa'i skyon spangs skye la dbang mdzad pa'i //
NK016(ma)008:382: khro chen h+aum k+aa ra la ma byin len spangs yo byad dbang mdzad pa'i //
NK016(ma)008:383: khro chen rnam par rgyal la srog gcod skyon spangs tshe la dbang mdzad pa //
NK016(ma)008:384: khro chen gshin rje gshed la phra ma'i skyon spangs chos la dbang mdzad pa //
NK016(ma)008:385: khro chen rta mchog dpal la ngag rtsub skyon spangs las la dbang mdzad pa //
NK016(ma)008:386: khro chen bdud rtsi 'khyil la log lta'i skyon spangs ye shes dbang mdzad pa //
NK016(ma)008:387: khro chen dbyug sngon can la rdzun gyi skyon spangs chos la dbang mdzad pa //
NK016(ma)008:388: khro chen mi g.yo mgon la ngag 'khyal skyon spangs sems la dbang mdzad pa //
NK016(ma)008:389: khro chen 'dod pa'i rgyal la phyag gnod sems skyon spangs rdzu 'phrul dbang mdzad pa //
NK016(ma)008:390: khro chen khams gsum rgyal la phyag brnab sems skyon spangs smon lam dbang mdzad pa //
NK016(ma)008:391: khro chen stobs po che la ye shes pha rol phyin ma ste //
NK016(ma)008:392: sgra 'byin ma la phyag shes rab pha rol phyin ma ste //
NK016(ma)008:393: rnam snyems ma la phyag tshul khrims pha rol phyin ma ste //
NK016(ma)008:394: rdo rje sder la phyag bsam gtan pha rol phyin ma ste //
NK016(ma)008:395: dur khrod ma la phyag thabs kyi pha rol phyin ma ste //
NK016(ma)008:396: gtun khung ma la phyag brtson 'grus pha rol phyin ma ste //
NK016(ma)008:397: rab gtum ma la phyag sbyin pa'i pha rol phyin ma ste //
NK016(ma)008:398: mda' snyems ma la phyag smon la ma pha rol phyin ma ste //
NK016(ma)008:399: bskyod byed ma la phyag stobs kyi pha rol phyin ma ste //
NK016(ma)008:400: gsod byed ma la phyag bzod pa'i pha rol phyin ma ste //
NK016(ma)008:401: bskul byed ma la phyag phyogs bcu dregs pa bsnol ba'i gdan steng na //
NK016(ma)008:402: ye shes bskal pa me dpung 'bar ba'i klong //
NK016(ma)008:403: bdud 'dul yab yum rnams la phyag dmigs med chos
NK016(ma)008:404: kyi sku la phyag longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la
NK016(ma)008:405: phyag cir yang sprul pa'i sku la phyag mi 'gyur
NK016(ma)008:406: rdo rje'i sku la phyag mngon par byang chub sku
NK016(ma)008:407: la phyag dus gsum rgyal ba rnams kyis bsgrubs pa
NK016(ma)008:408: yis // tshogs gnyis rdzogs shing yon tan mthar phyin pa'i //
NK016(ma)008:409: sku dang ye shes tshogs la phyag 'byung ba lnga las skur bzhengs pa //
NK016(ma)008:410: rtag pa'i rgyal mo lnga la phyag rang bzhin dbyings las grub pa mo //
NK016(ma)008:411: dbyings phyug lnga la phyag rgyu 'bras byang chub sems dpa'i sprul pa ste //
NK016(ma)008:412: mkha' 'gro sum cu gnyis la phyag 'tshal lo /
NK016(ma)008:413: ga na pa ti'i sprul pa ste //
NK016(ma)008:414: ging pho rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:415: lha mo dpal mo'i sprul pa ste //
NK016(ma)008:416: ging mo rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:417: 'jig rten khams la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK016(ma)008:419: 'dod pa'i ro la chags pa mo //
NK016(ma)008:420: ma mo'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:421: legs nyes stangs 'dzin dam tshig rjes gcod ma //
NK016(ma)008:422: bka' bzhin rjes su sgrub pa'i grogs mdzad ma //
NK016(ma)008:423: dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)008:424: a ti pu hoh pra ti pu hoh zhes bshags
NK016(ma)008:425: pa'i rgyud dri ma med pa'i rgyal po las phyag
